## The Right Approach: Full Redirect with JWT Handoff

Not an iframe. Full page navigation to the agentic dashboard, user lands already authenticated. Feels like one platform because the navigation is seamless. Each app keeps its own sidebar and layout.

The flow:

```
User in DPAH sidebar clicks "Analytics"
        ↓
DPAH calls GET /api/v1/auth/handoff-token
        ↓
Backend issues a short-lived token (60 seconds)
        ↓
Browser redirects to agentic dashboard URL with token in query param
        ↓
Agentic dashboard reads token, validates it, extracts emp_no + dept
        ↓
User sees agentic dashboard already logged in, correct department pre-selected
        ↓
Agentic dashboard has a "Back to DPAH" link in its sidebar
```

Total feeling: click Analytics → land in dashboard → click Back → return to DPAH. One platform.

